    "## Summary\n",
    "\n",
    "✅ **Key Takeaways:**\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **`torch.autograd.grad()`** is the primary tool for PINN derivatives\n",
    "2. **`create_graph=True`** enables higher-order derivatives\n",
    "3. **`retain_graph=True`** keeps graph for multiple gradient computations\n",
    "4. **`grad_outputs=torch.ones_like(y)`** needed for non-scalar outputs\n",
    "5. **Batch processing** works naturally - sum outputs for scalar gradients\n",
    "6. **Key PDE derivatives**: `u_t`, `u_x`, `u_xx`, `∇²u`, Jacobian, Hessian\n",
    "\n",
